{"id": 1562, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你觉得“假装有文化”的表现是什么？", "description": "快收手吧，真的文化人可不像你这样。（题图来自：Ana Matsusaki ​​​​）", "record_count": 8370, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170310124033WVSDsNCfL7vlJnMR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-16T03:00:58Z", "options": [{"id": 179456, "content": "借别人的书摆个拍?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131778}, {"id": 179457, "content": "各种问题都能回答的很有经验的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818146}, {"id": 185601, "content": "老梁故事汇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987004}, {"id": 179458, "content": "说起话来满嘴跑火车。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651741}, {"id": 179714, "content": "關注你平常不關注，關注了但從沒看過", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816267}, {"id": 182018, "content": "一本正经地胡说八道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648303}, {"id": 179459, "content": "不随便转发或点赞朋友圈，即使被人要求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160147}, {"id": 179715, "content": "是谈论国外咋了咋滴，是逛宜家，是崇洋媚外了还没觉出来的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940669}, {"id": 181251, "content": "火车上滔滔不绝地讲着自己的见闻，并坚定的以为那就是全世界。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867500}, {"id": 179460, "content": "喜欢李健", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972173}, {"id": 180228, "content": "上课不听 自拍照准备下课看 后来都删了", "image": "img/option/option/20170317221323THVuO7CeApYQ3EIa.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973620}, {"id": 179205, "content": "“我不是针对某个人，我的意思是，在座各位，________。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719650}, {"id": 179461, "content": "这里的很多人大概是自己真的没文化才会觉得别人做什么都是没文化的表现", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686179}, {"id": 179717, "content": "总是爱插嘴，总把吴晓波挂在嘴上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972672}, {"id": 179973, "content": "发自拍配鸡汤", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971083}, {"id": 181253, "content": "百度百科复制", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976397}, {"id": 181509, "content": "别人说某个话题时候，总会说就是那个谁，那啥，其实自己都不了解", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938073}, {"id": 182021, "content": "一定要和你不一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977760}, {"id": 182533, "content": "朋友圈你们都懂的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979312}, {"id": 179718, "content": "微博评论里以说教口吻对别人指手画脚还乱扣大帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 183558, "content": "别人说啥都装着会若有所思，然后都参与其中，最后还必须去自圆其说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981764}, {"id": 179207, "content": "常知其然而不知其所以然", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971662}, {"id": 179463, "content": "我们文化圈。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971851}, {"id": 179719, "content": "看着大家的各式总结 好想把那人一个个@出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 179208, "content": "某人好不容易看书 还没看一半就巴不得跟所有人分享心得?", "image": null, "praise_count": 576, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479814}, {"id": 179464, "content": "也许是我阅历不够，还真没发现", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851270}, {"id": 179720, "content": "对很多东西变得苛刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92975}, {"id": 184329, "content": "摘录书句标榜为自己的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983683}, {"id": 179210, "content": "在朋友圈转发热点新闻 长篇大论点评 但却没抓住新闻核心", "image": null, "praise_count": 187, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222898}, {"id": 179466, "content": "知乎：分享刚编的有文化的经历", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966543}, {"id": 179722, "content": "在猩爸读书做笔记的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786145}, {"id": 180490, "content": "鸡汤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966912}, {"id": 179211, "content": "知乎谢邀讲故事 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 607, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 179723, "content": "评论区基本都在假装有文化 懂得文化是什么吗？ 村上春树东野圭吾怎么惹到你们了？你们比他们有才华？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954522}, {"id": 182027, "content": "戴很多佛珠手串。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957825}, {"id": 198156, "content": "无端打压别人时惯用可以想象出这人趾高气扬的神态的词语，然而词语配进句子发出来时就像在告诉你她语文没学好似的，臭SB", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011736}, {"id": 179468, "content": "总在朋友圈发哪部书里的经典名句，但就是不知道他想表达什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743215}, {"id": 180493, "content": "文玩狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974363}, {"id": 179214, "content": "只知皮毛，不知其深意", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971806}, {"id": 180494, "content": "一知半解还爱抬杠，坚持自己只因自己有点印象", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958559}, {"id": 181262, "content": "一件事情只知道点皮毛，拼命说、重复说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976435}, {"id": 179215, "content": "貌似饱读诗书有什么，实际非常空洞，缺乏思想", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967490}, {"id": 179216, "content": "有文化假装不来", "image": null, "praise_count": 111, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258066}, {"id": 179472, "content": "去书店全顾着找角度拍照……会妨碍别人选书的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486711}, {"id": 179728, "content": "别人说什么都说早就自己知道了，如何如何，结果仔细一问，三不知。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496239}, {"id": 179217, "content": "对任何话题都爱插嘴，说一些一知半解的见解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841501}, {"id": 179729, "content": "不懂裝懂被拆穿⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767579}, {"id": 179985, "content": "名人去世前不知道，去世后就知道了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973187}, {"id": 180497, "content": "朋友圈发读书照片，其实只是买了新书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905664}, {"id": 179218, "content": "自封xx斋主，xx居士什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832815}]}